      "bbox": [
        148.74,
        439.01,
        190.45,
        450.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 3
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0041",
      "text": " In this state the FC frames transmitted by the N_Port are tagged with the",
      "bbox": [
        190.8,
        439.01,
        540.08,
        450.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 1,
      "span_index": 4
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0042",
      "text": "VFT_Header carrying VF_ID K. An FLOGI request, tagged with VF_ID K, is transmitted. This FLOGI",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        451.01,
        540.01,
        462.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 2,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0043",
      "text": "request shall carry the N_Port_Name of the Logical N_Port associated with VF_ID K and the opera-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        463.01,
        540.07,
        474.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 3,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0044",
      "text": "tional parameters (e.g., timeout values, Classes of service) of Virtual Fabric K. The FLOGI LS_ACC",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        475.01,
        540.04,
        486.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 4,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0045",
      "text": "assigns an N_Port_ID in Virtual Fabric K to the Logical N_Port associated with VF_ID K. All parame-",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        487.01,
        540.09,
        498.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 5,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0046",
      "text": "ters of the FLOGI request and the FLOGI LS_ACC transmitted in this state are used as specified in",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        499.01,
        539.92,
        510.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 6,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0047",
      "text": "clause 6, except that the following parameters in the Common Service Parameters are ignored and",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        511.01,
        539.89,
        522.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 7,
      "span_index": 1
    },
    {
      "span_id": "p205_s0048",
      "text": "the values transmitted in state P1 are used instead:",
      "bbox": [
        96.0,
        523.0,
        323.28,
        534.12
      ],
      "block_index": 12,
      "line_index": 8,
      "span_index": 1
    },
